RESTful.tt
----------

A T4 template to generate C# client code to consume RESTful web services in .NET 3.5SP1 and up.

Written by James Dunne <james.jdunne@gmail.com>

Features:
---------

* Simple; easy to use
* Descriptor-driven code generation
* Synchronous and asynchronous request execution
  * No dependency on TPL for asynchrony
* JSON serialization
* Free of memory leaks
